              </svg>
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              <p class="text-200 font-medium leading-tight desktop:text-300">
                Project Outsourcing
              </p>
              <p>
                Design and develop an innovative digital product and release it
                to market. Our dedicated development teams build custom web and
                mobile apps that meet the highest standards of the software
                development process. Suitable for new tech startups looking to
                launch and grow at speed
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col gap-3">
            <p>
              <svg
                class="h-8 w-8 desktop:h-12 desktop:w-12"
                width="48"
