            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              <p class="text-200 font-medium leading-tight desktop:text-300">
                Team Augmentation
              </p>
              <p>
                Let your digital products take advantage of our experts to build
                more robust features or to scale up current solutions. Suitable
                for businesses who already have a technical team surrounding
                their product, but need to hire a few talented engineers to
                augment their in-house team
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <footer class="bg-brand-500 py-2.5 text-center">
      <p class="text-50">©2023 Stellar Labs • All rights reserved</p>
    </footer>
